<title>SPAIN: Spain industrial gas price to fall sharply - reports.</title>
<headline>Spain industrial gas price to fall sharply - reports.</headline>
<dateline>MADRID 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Spanish industrial clients will pay 20 to 25 percent less for gas from June or July, local media quoted Energy Secretary Nemesio Fernandez Cuesta as saying on Thursday.</p>
<p>Industry Ministry officials were not available to comment.</p>
<p>Speaking in Castellon, the energy secretary said a bill aimed at liberalising the sector will be finalised before the summer, and a new system for calculation of the gas tariff will be introduced.</p>
<p>-- Madrid newsroom +341 585 2160</p>
